   <br/>
   <h1>NEXUS Engineering Ltd.</h1> 
   <p align="justify">NEXUS Engineering Ltd. is a privately owned and independently operating commercial company providing both field and laboratory inspection services. The firm was founded in 2004. It is located in Sofia, Bulgaria. The team members are highly qualified MS Engineers and/or EN-473 Level III and Level II certified specialists in non-destructive testing. The company provides services and solutions in the field of non-destructive testing and evaluation (NDT&amp;E) of materials and structures. We cover the whole range of activities from fundamental scientific studies through to the transfer of technology to industry.</p>
   <p align="justify">NEXUS Engineering activities include contact- and immersion-Ultrasonic testing, X-Ray and Gamma Ray radiography, Liquid Penetrant testing, Magnetic Particle inspection, Eddy Current flaw detection and material sorting, Visual inspection.</p>
   <p align="justify">NEXUS Engineering's company goal has always been to respond to our customers needs with the use of the most up-to-date procedures, processes, and by hiring qualified personnel in the industry.</p>
